{"tid":519711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九龍城26歲女子報稱遭兩外籍男輪姦 涉「報假案」被捕","createTime":"2018-01-04T15:43:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T03:19:54.000Z","uid":2748,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ad70f817ece387c13093dbf654dd15dcf626cea7","tid":519711,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T15:43:00.000Z","msg":"警方於去年大除夕（12月31日）上午約7時30分接獲一名26歲女子報案，指同日在九龍城區一大廈的梯間被兩名非華裔男子強姦。<br />\n<br />\n九龍城警區重案組人員接手調查，經深入調查後，相信該名女子虛構事件。重案組人員今日（4日）拘捕該名女子，涉嫌浪費警力。被捕女子將被通宵扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n#metoo<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c86d3d67a3130dd78db0f85f5f9faf5f40d80738","tid":519711,"uid":163031,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T15:44:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勞</span></span>"},{"pid":"d891bf1d0b46a8b8dd917bbfaa429b237ea05a43","tid":519711,"uid":81183,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T15:45:00.000Z","msg":"乜野係非華裔<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n南<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd99329b39f5cc118240e4f343383fbe7f172375","tid":519711,"uid":21995,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T15:45:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/33/2016/04/11/0/0f9e1dcb0e6515b7a3a89cbca5b0428f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F33%2F2016%2F04%2F11%2F0%2F0f9e1dcb0e6515b7a3a89cbca5b0428f.jpg&h=04608d56&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1fa9e3c12b83b29101dc6e440d994b32e495cd3","tid":519711,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d891bf1d0b46a8b8dd917bbfaa429b237ea05a43","tid":519711,"uid":81183,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T15:45:00.000Z","msg":"乜野係非華裔<img